      <title>奥拉电气说要削减一千个工作岗位以阻止损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ola-electric-said-to-cut-over-a-thousand-jobs-to-stem-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，Ola Electric Mobility Ltd.正在裁员一千多名员工和合同工人，因为印度顶级踏板车制造商之一竞选削减损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ola-electric-said-to-cut-over-a-thousand-jobs-to-stem-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 05:24:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着DeepSeek加热AI，阿里巴巴支持的Zhipu筹集了1.4亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/alibaba-backed-zhipu-raises-140-million-as-deepseek-heats-up-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国初创公司Zhipu筹集了超过10亿元人民币（1.4亿美元），这是由地方政府支持的公司领导的一轮融资，强调了DeepSeek的上升后对国内AI的日益增长的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/alibaba-backed-zhipu-raises-140-million-as-deepseek-heats-up-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 04:22:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
